<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ṭbyby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- yạ ṭbyby hạt dwạyạ wdwạyạ tkwn
 mʿạyạ fy ḥyạty fy ṭryqy
 ạ̹nt rby wṣdyqy wạ̹nt nwry fy ạlḥyạẗ wạ̹nt
 frḥy whnạyạ
 yạ ạ̹lhy yạ ḥbyby yạ ṭbyby yạ yswʿ
 1- yạ ṭbyby njĩ nfsy m ạlsẖrwr wạlạ̉tẖạm
 nqĩ qlby m ạlkẖṭyẗ wạmlạh kẖyr wslạm
 kẖd bạ̹ydy fy ṭryqk fy ḥyạty mạly gẖyrk
 ạ̉ḥn qlb ạ̉wfy̱ ṣdyq ṭbyb sẖạfy llậlạm
 yạ ṭbyby hạt dwạyạ yạ ḥbyby mʿạk sẖfạyạ
 yạ ạ̹lhy yạ ḥbyby yạ ṭbyby yạ yswʿ
 2- yạ ṭbyb ạhdy nfsy mn ạḍṭrạbạt ạlḥyạẗ</lyrics>
<author>ʿmạd ryạḍ, ʿmạd ryạḍ</author>
